    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">ASR Outdoors collapsible lanterns are available in two sizes, and provide 360 degree dense bright white, high quality, uniform lighting for camping, road tripping, if you’re stuck in a power outage, boating, hiking and more.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 100 Lumen COB Collapsible Camping Lantern Black or Grey (2 Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>ASR Outdoors collapsible lanterns are available in two sizes, and provide 360 degree dense bright white, high quality, uniform lighting for camping, road tripping, if you’re stuck in a power outage, boating, hiking and more.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>CAMPING LANTERNS:</strong> Featuring 100 or 200 Lumen brightness and COB technology, these camping lanterns provide 360 degree bright white, high quality, uniform lighting for camping, hiking, backpacking, trekking and more</li>\n    <li><strong>COMPACT AND COLLPASIBLE DESIGN:</strong> Unique collapsible design is easy to use; to turn on, simply pull up on the handles and the light will automatically illuminate; to turn off, simply push down on the top of the lantern and the light will automatically shut off</li>\n    <li><strong>EMERGENCY SUPPLIES:</strong> A must have emergency preparedness item to include with a survival kit, disaster preparedness kit or roadside emergency car kit when there’s no access to power or electricity; batteries are included with all camping lanterns making them ready to go right out of the box</li>\n    <li><strong>HANGING LANTERN:</strong> Camping lamp includes two foldaway handles on the exterior body of the lantern for convenient and lightweight portability, as well as easy suspension in a tent or campsite, for low light trails or just about anywhere you need light</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Large Dimensions: 7.25 inches expanded, 5 inches collapsed; Small Dimensions: 5.5 inches expanded, 4.0 inches collapsed</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/73004/72RlMKeFNpXD5zawtRIZ7CgR3htjUH-metaY29sbGFwc19sYW50ZXJuc19wYXJlbnQuanBn-.jpg?expires=1750280399&amp;signature=a211c31ea14ba1fdeb95641d0f99678ad0828cdebbc208ee6029cc44ff60062c\" alt=\"ASR Outdoors collapsible lanterns are available in two sizes, and provide 360 degree dense bright white, high quality, uniform lighting for camping\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p>Equipped with COB technology, the camping lanterns have long lasting bulbs and come with batteries preinstalled, making them conveniently ready to use right out of the box. In addition, the outdoor lights feature a unique collapsible design, giving you control over the luminosity output, allowing for easy adjustments depending on how much you light you need across different indoor or outdoor scenarios. The camping lanterns also have built in, foldaway handles on the exterior body of the lantern, making them portable and quick to hang if needed; their compact sizes when fully collapsed contributes to their longevity and durability, while also making them lightweight and easy to tote packed, or hooked to the exterior of outdoor gear with a carabiner (not included).</p>\n  <p>An outdoor essential, these collapsible outdoor lights can help prep a meal in the dark, make the perfect reading light in your tent, create ambiance for late night camp games and act as a staple in your roadside emergency car kit or general emergency supplies. And yes, you could just use a flashlight or headlamp, but these lightweight, portable adjustable lanterns make all your two handed tasks easier and more efficient.</p>\n  <p>Large Lantern Dimensions Open: 7.25 inches Large Lantern Dimensions Collapsed: 5 inches Small Lantern Dimensions Open: 5.5 inches Small Lantern Dimensions Collapsed: 3.25 inches</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
